data.description: DON’T MAKE A MOVE WITHOUT scheduling a visit to this amazing home! If you are looking for a super spacious ranch, you have just found it. Loaded with updates from top to bottom, inside and out. The updated kitchen features gorgeous maple cabinets, granite counters, stainless appliances and tile back splash. Immaculate, refinished hardwood floors, updated windows, newer furnace, hot water heater and central air. Nicely updated bath and so much more!  Unfinished basement is spotless and ready for your own transformation. The enormous private, fenced yard is just gorgeous. 3 season sunroom that could be easily converted into a 4 season for added living space. Attached garage, storage shed, large concrete patio. Conveniently located just a short distance from the several headquarters , restaurants, shopping and schools. Keys at closing.
